<br>
They floated around the back of the tower and found the teleport that would grant them entry.  Once inside, all was quiet.  Too quiet.   Myth looked down the hall and saw a pair of spectre-like creatures guarding some entry.  There were only two so he believed they could take them.  He looked into his warder's eyes and bade him to guard their location with his life.  The warder acknowledged this but his ears perked up.  He really wanted to explore.<br>
<br>
Mythalen raised his arm and a mystical spear of ice appeared in his hand.  He hurled it across the roam and the spectres came.  The group dispatched these beasts with little problem.  Mythalen then began going room by room to clear the area.   On the third room, he returned to find that disaster struck.  His warder was missing!<br>
<br>
He looked all around and then saw it.  His pup was sliding across the floor chasing two spectres, three skeletons, and a huge undead gnoll-like abomination.  They were all running right at Mythalen.<br>
<br>
Mythalen looked at Rhyanna, &quot;If this gets ugly, get out.&quot;  The battle began and it seemed to be going well, for a short time.  Then Mythalen came to the grim realization that this could not be won.  He told his warder and Rhyanna to escape.  He held the creatures at bay as long as he could before he rushed out of the tower.<br>
<br>
Once outside his warder looked oh so innocently up at its master.  Mythalen reached to ruffle its fur when he was attacked by four apparitions!  He screamed for Rhyanna to get to safety and led the apparitions off on a chase.  He was bleeding profusely by the time he reached the pirate camp.  A group of adventurers were there to fight off the beasts and Mythalen passed out without knowing what became of his beloved warder or Rhyanna, the woman he had grown to love. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub149.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lanadena>Lanadena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Chieftess of Norrath</span><br>  Posts: 3236<br> <font color=#330000>(2/13/03 2:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p203.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1935.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lessons learned in the black tower</span><hr size=1> /ooc<br>
